{"segment_id": "shijing__song-shangsong-005__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-shangsong-005", "source_id": "song-shangsong-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·商頌·005.1", "text_original": "撻彼殷武，奮伐荊楚，冞入其阻，裒荊之旅。\n有截其所，湯孫之緒。", "text_normalized": "撻彼殷武，奮伐荊楚，冞入其阻，裒荊之旅。\n有截其所，湯孫之緒。", "notes": "殷武 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-shangsong-005__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-shangsong-005", "source_id": "song-shangsong-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·商頌·005.2", "text_original": "維女荊楚，居國南鄉，昔有成湯，自彼氐羌。\n莫敢不來享，莫敢不來王，曰商是常。", "text_normalized": "維女荊楚，居國南鄉，昔有成湯，自彼氐羌。\n莫敢不來享，莫敢不來王，曰商是常。", "notes": "殷武 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-shangsong-005__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-shangsong-005", "source_id": "song-shangsong-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·商頌·005.3", "text_original": "天命多辟，設都于禹之績。\n歲事來辟，勿予禍適，稼穡匪解。", "text_normalized": "天命多辟，設都于禹之績。\n歲事來辟，勿予禍適，稼穡匪解。", "notes": "殷武 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-shangsong-005__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-shangsong-005", "source_id": "song-shangsong-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·商頌·005.4", "text_original": "天命降監，下民有嚴，不僭不濫，不敢怠遑。\n命于下國，封建厥福。", "text_normalized": "天命降監，下民有嚴，不僭不濫，不敢怠遑。\n命于下國，封建厥福。", "notes": "殷武 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-shangsong-005__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-shangsong-005", "source_id": "song-shangsong-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·商頌·005.5", "text_original": "商邑翼翼，四方之極，赫赫厥聲，濯濯厥靈。\n壽考且寧，以保我後生。", "text_normalized": "商邑翼翼，四方之極，赫赫厥聲，濯濯厥靈。\n壽考且寧，以保我後生。", "notes": "殷武 Chinese stanza 5."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-shangsong-005__006__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-shangsong-005", "source_id": "song-shangsong-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·商頌·005.6", "text_original": "陟彼景山，松柏丸丸，是斷是遷，方斵是虔。\n松桷有梴，旅楹有閑，寢成孔安。", "text_normalized": "陟彼景山，松柏丸丸，是斷是遷，方斵是虔。\n松桷有梴，旅楹有閑，寢成孔安。", "notes": "殷武 Chinese stanza 6."}
